ce/airpc-engine/.ai-workflow-v2-refine8/logs/verify-1784721750637.log\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  19278 Jul 22 20:02 /Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/.ai-workflow-v2-refine8/logs/verify-1784721742607.log\ntotal 2568\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  81113 Jul 23 09:24 latest-verify.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  81113 Jul 23 09:24 batch-14-1784769881446.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  80881 Jul 23 09:12 batch-13-1784769138678.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  80755 Jul 23 09:04 batch-12-1784768682420.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff   3552 Jul 22 21:23 latest-block-analysis.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  80224 Jul 22 20:09 batch-11-1784722154608.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  80169 Jul 22 20:02 batch-10-1784721756099.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  80156 Jul 22 19:56 batch-9-1784721399009.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  80153 Jul 22 19:33 batch-8-1784720028368.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  80156 Jul 22 19:27 batch-7-1784719656676.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  79627 Jul 22 19:01 batch-6-1784718085719.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  81310 Jul 22 18:52 batch-5-1784717541624.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  79997 Jul 22 18:46 batch-4-1784717171239.json\n-rw-r--r--  1 bolbiao  staff  80093 Jul 22 18:40 batch-3-1784716833193.json\n","localExecutionTimeMs":86},"isBackground":false},"description":"Tail executor log; list recent verify reports"},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-25bbc289-82a4-444d-96bb-fcdab012335d-19\nfc_faed24ab-8e7e-9dcb-90e4-b138915ef5df_2","startedAtMs":"1784770551763","completedAtMs":"1784770552811"},"model_call_id":"30490029-fc72-4335-8f87-781f5133ca7f-4-gnbw","session_id":"daa01eab-40eb-4095-b01d-e1075e6bc81e","timestamp_ms":1784770552764}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-25bbc289-82a4-444d-96bb-fcdab012335d-22\nfc_faed24ab-8e7e-9dcb-90e4-b138915ef5df_5","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","offset":400,"limit":40},"result":{"success":{"content":"\n**角色真源**仅 `data/characters/<agentId>.json`。「本包用到谁」由 `cards[].ownerAgentId`、effects 内 `agentId`、attach 目标归属等**派生**，**禁止**把 `participants` 当白名单或作者手维护清单。\n\n**禁止**在包内维护 `agents[]` 第二份角色定义（避免与 `data/characters/` 双真源）。显示名 / Free 卡一律读角色库。\n\n完整 JSON 字段见卡文件；包目录与分文件约定见 [07](../技术设计文档/07-壳嵌入与导出契约.md)、[19 §3](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)。  \n**磁盘真源**：`story.conf.json` 的 `cards[]` 仅为索引；上表 `cards: CallCardDefinition[]` 表示 Host **组装后的逻辑视图**，非单文件内联编辑真源。\n\n### 8.1 Schedule 落盘分工（钉死）\n\n| 用途 | 落盘 | 运行 `packageId` | 谁维护 |\n|------|------|------------------|--------|\n| 角色日常 / 周期性外呼目标 | `data/characters/schedule-cards/<cardId>.s-card.json` | `__schedule__` | 角色库 / 专用路径（Studio `POST /api/schedule-cards`） |\n| 故事包内剧情调度节点 | `data/storis-packages/<pkg>/cards/<cardId>.s-card.json`（`cardKind=schedule`） | 真实故事包 id | 故事编辑器画布 |\n\n铁律：\n\n1. `schedule_recurring_call` 的目标**只**认 `scheduleCardId` → `characters/schedule-cards/`，或 `cardId` + `packageId=__schedule__`（同目录）；可选 `__free__` 下 free/schedule fallback。\n2. **禁止**把故事包内 `cardKind=schedule` 节点当作 recurring 目标（校验 `SCHEDULE_CARD_KIND`）。\n3. StoryCard 上挂 `schedule_recurring_call` → `SCHEDULE_RECURRING_IN_STORY` error。\n4. 画布把卡改成 `cardKind=schedule` 仍写回**本包** `cards/`（剧情节点）；日常调度卡必须走 schedule-cards 专用创建口，不得只靠改 cardKind「伪装」。\n\n详见 [19 §3.4](../技术设计文档/19-引擎宿主与会话模型.md)、[08](./08-内容校验规则.md) SCHEDULE_*。\n\n## 9. Outcome（通话结果，供条件使用）\n\n```ts\ntype OutcomeFlag =\n  | \"answered_completed\"    // 正常接通并结束\n  | \"missed\"                // 未接\n  | \"busy\"                  // 占线\n  | \"hangup_early\"          // 提前挂断\n  | \"playback_completed\"    // 过场播放完成\n  | \"playback_skipped\"\n  | \"user_redial_pressed\"   // 用户按重播（作为独立模拟事件时）\n  | \"voicemail_listened\"\n  | \"callback_fired\"        // 调度的回拨已触发\n  | \"timeout\"\n\ninterface Outcome {","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":449,"fileSize":17454,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/需求/01-CallCard数据模型.md","readRange":{"startLine":400,"endLine":439},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-25bbc289-82a4-444d-96bb-fcdab012335d-22\nfc_faed24ab-8e7e-9dcb-90e4-b138915ef5df_5","startedAtMs":"1784770552623","completedAtMs":"1784770552812"},"model_call_id":"30490029-fc72-4335-8f87-781f5133ca7f-4-gnbw","session_id":"daa01eab-40eb-4095-b01d-e1075e6bc81e","timestamp_ms":1784770552765}
